It&apos;s not blocking, but something to consider...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also: this patch includes the contents of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2066&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2066&lt;/a&gt;. The new files are:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; .../apache/pig/IteratingAccumulatorEvalFunc.java&lt;br/&gt;
 .../udf/evalfunc/IteratingAccumulatorCount.java&lt;br/&gt;
 .../udf/evalfunc/IteratingAccumulatorIsEmpty.java&lt;br/&gt;
 .../test/udf/evalfunc/IteratingAccumulatorSum.java&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;And of course, new e2e tests in nightly.conf&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
